{"tid":1469813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原來係余若薇胞弟 余若海代機管局申請個禁制令","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:17:46.000Z","uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a6674ec9edae8d02c82356a1f8b54ae075ad9927","tid":1469813,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:10:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3987769 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F3987769%20&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0UPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=4228bd28\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3987769 </a><br />\n<br />\n今天凌晨傳出消息，香港機管局透過大律師余若海，向香港高等法院申請禁制令。香港機管局早上說，正在取得有關臨時禁制令的蓋印副本中，並會在取得有關蓋印副本後展示該臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.dwnews.com/china/news/2019-08-13/60145178.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.dwnews.com%2Fchina%2Fnews%2F2019-08-13%2F60145178.html&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0UPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=0a5df17b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.dwnews.com/china/news/2019-08-13/60145178.html</a><br />\n<br />\n臨時禁制令清楚表明，不可理解臨時禁制令為批准任何有違反公安條例的示威、抗議或公眾活動。機場管理局正在取得有關臨時禁制令的蓋印副本中，並會在取得有關蓋印副本後展示該臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，13日約9時30分，包括資深大律師餘若海等數名律師突然現身法庭，高院七樓約在晚上22時，曾在內庭開庭處理，但該案並不公開，記者亦未能入內。餘若海等人於晚上22時30分左右離開法庭，未有透露內容，他的律師團則約23時離開，同樣未發一言，亦未有透露是否就機場情況作任何緊急申請<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4E64Gg8OdcgIZHEd2T.gUA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDA0O2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/news_photo_A06c_new01x04201115copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4E64Gg8OdcgIZHEd2T.gUA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDA0O2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2Fnews_photo_A06c_new01x04201115copy.jpg&h=27132128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e1383215f7ad7fa4fd91b5efe338baf48ac7d97","tid":1469813,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7d3ed57af8a20cd3b588d4944c1bc58c634434","tid":1469813,"uid":204295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"所以？"},{"pid":"6a02c9d7302e1bc0766eb33964174e41d00bf4f5","tid":1469813,"uid":6165,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"家姐正常唔代表細路係好人"},{"pid":"0b508db9fa7a536ef10aa59533fb2bd927e03f95","tid":1469813,"uid":204295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"Cab-rank Rule"},{"pid":"804c2ba1a8520f26753a2ae150fbbed5ea76328c","tid":1469813,"uid":28257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc7d3ed57af8a20cd3b588d4944c1bc58c634434","tid":1469813,"uid":204295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"所以？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:28.000Z","msg":"冇咩所以 新聞內容 禁制令的詳情姐<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月3日，於青年新政立法會議員宣誓案中，余若海於法庭說根據中文維基百科中對於支那的解釋，港獨支持者經常使用支那一詞，加上梁頌恆宣誓時手指交叉，代表講一些不是本意的說話，因而有理由相信兩人借宣誓鼓吹港獨，有關行為表現已構成拒絕宣誓"},{"pid":"e2a0ef55fa015027a5c5b12232b050015092e505","tid":1469813,"uid":225056,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"的士站原則<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/的士站原則\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%AB%99%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0UPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=f0c58e2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/的士站原則</a><br />\n<br />\n的士站原則（英文：Cab-rank rule），又稱驛站原則、不得拒聘原則，是實施普通法的地區對執業大律師規管的一項原則：執業大律師接到案件後，除非存在利益衝突，否則只要當事人能夠支付費用，便必須接受委聘。"},{"pid":"c37cd8d4710bbb94796257aad8619a08fd213544","tid":1469813,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"黑 警 機 場 拔 槍 指 嚇 示 威 者 ！ 同 你 逐 格 睇 暨 聽 日 文 宣 方 向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br 